    93â†’### Session Management
    95â†’Maintain conversation context:
    96â†’
    97â†’```go
    98â†’// First message
    99â†’host.Prompt(ctx, "My name is Alice")
   100â†’
   101â†’// Second message (remembers context)
   102â†’response, _ := host.Prompt(ctx, "What's my name?")
   103â†’// Response: "Your name is Alice"
   104â†’
   105â†’// Save session
   106â†’host.SaveSession("./session.json")
