   115â†’## API Reference
   117â†’### Types
   119â†’- `MCPHost` - Main SDK type
   120â†’- `Options` - Configuration options
   121â†’- `Message` - Conversation message
   122â†’- `ToolCall` - Tool invocation details
   123â†’
   124â†’### Methods
   126â†’- `New(ctx, opts)` - Create new MCPHost instance
   127â†’- `Prompt(ctx, message)` - Send message and get response
   128â†’- `PromptWithCallbacks(ctx, message, ...)` - Send message with progress callbacks
   129â†’- `LoadSession(path)` - Load session from file
   130â†’- `SaveSession(path)` - Save session to file
   131â†’- `ClearSession()` - Clear conversation history
   132â†’- `GetSessionManager()` - Get session manager for advanced usage
   133â†’- `GetModelString()` - Get current model string
   134â†’- `Close()` - Clean up resources
   135â†’
   136â†’## Environment Variables
   138â†’All CLI environment variables work with the SDK:
   139â†’
   140â†’- `MCPHOST_MODEL` - Override model
   141â†’- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - Anthropic API key
   142â†’- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API key
   143â†’- `GEMINI_API_KEY` - Google API key
   144â†’- etc.
   145â†’
   146â†’## License
   148â†’Same as MCPHost CLI

